  <brief_title>Saginil in vs. Placebo for Gynecologic Oncology Patients Affected by Vaginitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Saginil in Vaginal Cannulas vs. Placebo for the Prevention of Vaginitis in Gynecologic Oncologic Patients Receiving Chemotherapy: a Randomized Controlled Trial.</official_title>
