  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      We hypothesise that the use of Adelmidrol (Saginil in vaginal cannulas) can reduce the
      incidence and magnitude of vaginitis in patients affected by gynecologic malignancies.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
